channel.title: Project King C r 0 w N!
channel.description:
Hello , I will be starting a project named Pkc short for Project King Cr0wn. This will involve a lot of coding and time. You may learn from this and enjoy or may not learn anything but you must enjoy. I am looking for people that don't slack , for example our coder Frugoo Scape. He will be coding my server and Sick Of Air will be on the administator list. If you want to join these are the jobs available :
Coders - Will code the server to improve it. I don't want horrible coders , I want coders that know what they are doing and on task at all times.
Tester - Testers will play to see if the update in skill/minigame/anything else has worked 100 percent no glitches. If a coder has found glitches they must report to me immediatly or else the server won't be that great.
Client Maker - Will make the client to play on , mostly looking for 377 cache.
Client Designer - Will design the client to interest people with just looking at it ^.^
Idea Makers - Will make idea's up , as I don't have a good imagination. All idea's must be approved by me or an administator. Don't think of anything stupid because we will say no and will not listen to your idea's . Chance of getting fired as well.
I will not give admin , mod , co-owner jobs due to the fact I don't like power hunger noobs that just abuse their powers.
Forums : Almost done :D Server completion : 10 percent
There will be levels of jobs as well. I will write them down and you will reveiw them.
Knows a little - Level one - Will be assigned in a red color Knows his stuff but not that great - Level 2 - Will be assigned a yellow color Knows his stuff - Level 3 - Will be assigned a orange color A medium type person - Level 4 - Will be assigned a purple color A good person - Level 5 - Will be assigned a pink color A awesome person - Level 6 - Will be assigned a blue color A master - Level 7 - Will be assigned a brown color Legendary (The hardest of all) - Level 8 - Will be assigned a teal color!
As you know our color codes , time to get into our next buisness...How to join? There are forms for coders , testers and others.
Tester Application : Username : How long will you be on moparscape ? : Will you be there for every test event ? : Experience : Accept [--] Decline [--]
Coder Application : Username : How long have you coded? : What would you rate yourself ? : How long will you be online? : Are you considered a good coder? : Accept [--] Decline [--]
Client Coder and Designer : Username : Have you ever coded a client? If so what type of cache ? : How long will you be online ? : Will you inspire people with your amazment? : Accept [--] Decline [--]
Idea Makers Application : Username : How long will you be on moparscape a day? : Do you have a wise imagination? : Will you think of real possible things to add? : Rate your imagination : ?/10 Accept [--] Decline [--]
Leave the accept and decline box alone. Do not touch. Anyone that lies to proof to look good will be fired as once. If you be honest you are likely to be chosen. If you have an issue about this server don't complain because flaming doesn't get you anywhere except banned.
[center] [u]Testers[/u] -Open -Open -Open
[u]Coders[/u] -Frugoo Scape -P I M P 3 D Tut -doggiedoo86 -Inmate™ -Open
[u]Client Designer[/u] - O M G [dakota] -Open Designers - Combine your work together to make some amazing
[u]Client Maker[/u] -O M G [dakota] -Open
[u]Idea makers[/u] -trackerofdeath4500 -Open -Open
[/center]
Sick Of Air , Frugoo Scape and I are admins on the forums and in game. Do not ask for admins and do not ask them for admins. <33
[b]If you do not like my source please leave and don't end up in trouble because of flaming!![/b] My source is project 16 soon to be Project KingCr0wn!
Anyone is available to join even CM's , Mod's , and Vet's. This isn't just for regular people it's for everyone to learn a little java and have fun with yourself :)
Thank you for listening , King C R 0 W N
